# ‚ùì Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

## What is LLM Studio?
LLM Studio is a platform that enables users to design, generate, and deploy decentralized applications powered by large language model orchestration.

## Who can use LLM Studio?
Developers, blockchain enthusiasts, and enterprises looking to create decentralized applications with AI integration can use LLM Studio.

## Do I need programming experience?
Basic understanding of programming is helpful, but our intuitive interface and templates significantly lower the barrier to entry.

## Which blockchains does LLM Studio support?
Initially, we support Ethereum and Binance Smart Chain, with plans to expand to other major chains like Polygon and Solana.

## How secure is LLM Studio?
Security is a top priority. We implement multiple security audits, best practices in smart contract design, and monitoring tools.

## Is there a fee to use the platform?
Certain features have transaction fees, paid using our native token, but the core design and testing tools are free.

## What is the role of the native token?
The token is used for transaction fees, governance voting, rewards, and unlocking premium features.

## Can I contribute to LLM Studio?
Yes, we encourage community contributions through open-source projects, feedback, and participation in governance.

## How often is LLM Studio updated?
We follow a quarterly update cycle with continuous patches and minor improvements as needed.

## Where can I find documentation and support?
Documentation is available on our official GitBook, and support is provided via our community forums and Discord.

## Will LLM Studio support NFTs and DeFi?
Yes, future updates will include specialized modules for NFT creation and DeFi protocols.

## How does LLM orchestration work?
LLM orchestration coordinates multiple language model agents to perform tasks within decentralized applications, enhancing decision-making and automation.

## What are the system requirements?
LLM Studio is cloud-based; users require a modern browser and internet connection for the best experience.

## How is user data handled?
We prioritize privacy and comply with data protection regulations, storing minimal user data with encryption.

## What is the roadmap for new features?
Refer to our roadmap document for detailed timelines and upcoming initiatives.

For any further questions, please reach out to our support team or community channels.